title: Intel’s new Core i9-12900KS is the world’s fastest desktop CPU with up to 5.5Ghz speed
content:
Intel’s new 12th gen Alder Lake chips have already made huge waves in the industry but it looks like it’s not done yet. The company just announced a new member of its 12th gen Alder Lake desktop CPU family, the Core i9-12900KS. According to Intel, the new special edition Core i9-12900KS is the world’s fastest

description: Intel has announced the new Core i9-12900KS processor. According to the company, this is now the world's fastest desktop processor.
